---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Logo from "../components/Logo.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — troniti">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24">
    <div class="mb-12 flex justify-center">
      <Logo size="lg" />
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-text-muted">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 text-text-muted">
      <section>
        <p>troniti (this website, troniti.com) is a non-custodial TRON yield-management service. This policy explains the limited information we process when you visit this site or join the waitlist. troniti is non-custodial: we never hold your funds or private keys, and we do not have access to your wallet.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>This site does not require an account. The only personal data we collect is what you voluntarily provide:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-inside list-disc space-y-1">
          <li>Your email address, if you submit it to join the waitlist</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We do not currently run third-party analytics or advertising trackers on this site. Standard server logs may be retained by our hosting provider.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">How We Use This Data</h2>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-1">
          <li>To contact you about troniti's launch and onboarding, if you joined the waitlist</li>
          <li>To improve the site's content and presentation</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We do not sell your data and we do not display advertising on this site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Your Choices</h2>
        <p>Providing your email is optional. To have your email removed from the waitlist at any time, contact us at the address below.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this policy, reach us on X at <a href="https://x.com/ahmlvs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">@ahmlvs</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-text">&larr; Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
